For no prophecy was ever produced by will of man but men spoke from YHWH as they were carried along by Holy Spirit. And we have prophetic word more fully confirmed to which you will do well to pay attention as to lamp shining in dark place until day dawns and morning star rises in your hearts knowing this first of all that no prophecy of Scripture comes from someone’s own interpretation.
For when He received honor and glory from YHWH the Father and voice was borne to Him by Majestic Glory “This is My beloved Son with whom I am well pleased” we ourselves heard this very voice borne from heaven for we were with Him on holy mountain. For we did not follow cleverly devised myths when we made known to you power and coming of our Lord Yeshua the Anointed but we were eyewitnesses of His majesty.
And I will make every effort so that after my departure you may be able at any time to recall these things. For I know that putting off of my body will be soon as our Lord Yeshua the Anointed made clear to me. And I will make every effort so that after my departure you may be able at any time to recall these things.
For this reason I will not be negligent to remind you of these things though you know them and are established in present truth. I think it right as long as I am in this body to stir you up by way of reminder.
For if these qualities are yours and are increasing they keep you from being ineffective or unfruitful in knowledge of our Lord Yeshua the Anointed. For whoever lacks these qualities is so nearsighted that he is blind having forgotten that he was cleansed from his former sins. Therefore brothers be all more diligent to confirm your calling and election for if you practice these qualities you will never fall. For in this way there will be richly provided for you entrance into eternal kingdom of our Lord and Savior Yeshua the Anointed.
And knowledge with self-control and self-control with steadfastness and steadfastness with godliness and godliness with brotherly affection and brotherly affection with love. For this very reason make every effort to supplement your faith with virtue and virtue with knowledge.
His divine power has granted to us all things that pertain to life and godliness through knowledge of Him who called us to His own glory and excellence by which He has granted to us His precious and very great promises so that through them you may become partakers of divine nature having escaped corruption that is in world because of sinful desire.
Simeon Peter servant and apostle of Yeshua the Anointed. To those who have obtained faith of equal standing with ours by righteousness of our YHWH and Savior Yeshua the Anointed. May grace and peace be multiplied to you in knowledge of YHWH and of Yeshua our Lord.

